				<ext:value>description-en:
On this lobby card for the Hindi movie  &quot;Satyam Shivam Sundaram&quot; released in 1978, Zeenat Aman can be seen ringing a bell at the entrance of a temple, dressed in a white sari. In the background, several men wearing pink turbans can be seen. (gs/tb/sp)</ext:value>
